OL,3,CFirst closed grooming gang cases
OL,4,Creturned to police for reinvestigation
OL,6,FEight closed grooming gang cases are
OL,7,Fthe first to be reopened as part of a
OL,8,Fnational review of hundreds of
OL,9,Finvestigations in which lines of
OL,10,Finquiry may have been overlooked due
OL,11,Fto human error.
OL,13,FNational policing initiative Operation
OL,14,FBeaconport was launched last year to
OL,15,Freview hundreds of previously closed
OL,16,Finvestigations into child exploitation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
