OL,3,CFirst closed grooming gang cases
OL,4,Creturned to police for reinvestigation
OL,6,FIt is examining cases between January
OL,7,F1, 2010 and March 31, 2025, involving
OL,8,Ftwo or more suspects, more than one
OL,9,Fvictim, contact offences, where the
OL,10,Fsuspects are still alive, and which
OL,11,Fhave not already been independently
OL,12,Freviewed.
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FThousands are expected to come under
OL,20,Fscrutiny.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
