OL,3,CFirst closed grooming gang cases
OL,4,Creturned to police for reinvestigation
OL,6,FIn November, 1,273 investigations from
OL,7,F23 police forces had already been
OL,8,Freferred to the National Crime Agency
OL,9,Fteam, 236 of which were prioritised
OL,10,Fbecause they involved allegations of
OL,11,Frape.
OL,13,FNCA director general Graeme Biggar
OL,14,Fsaid: "Operation Beaconport is the
OL,15,Fmost comprehensive and complex
OL,16,Finvestigation into child sexual
OL,17,Fexploitation and abuse in UK history.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
