PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781608793
OL,3,CFirst closed grooming gang cases
OL,4,Creturned to police for reinvestigation
OL,6,F"After months of careful joint work
OL,7,Fwith policing to lay the foundations,
OL,8,Fwe have sent the first cases back to
OL,9,Fforces to be reopened. This is the
OL,10,Ffirst step toward seeking justice for
OL,11,Fvictims and survivors.
OL,13,F"An investigation of this magnitude
OL,14,Fwill take time. Operation Beaconport
OL,15,Fis working with determination to get
OL,16,Fit right for victims and survivors."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@dO]
