PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781608793
OL,3,CFirst closed grooming gang cases
OL,4,Creturned to police for reinvestigation
OL,6,FOperation Beaconport, which was
OL,7,Frecommended in Baroness Casey's major
OL,8,Freview of grooming gangs, is led by
OL,9,Fthe National Crime Agency in
OL,10,Fcollaboration with the National Police
OL,11,FChiefs' Council (NPCC), the Child
OL,12,FSexual Exploitation (CSE) Taskforce
OL,13,Fand the TOEX Programme to address past
OL,14,Ffailures and ensure complex cases of
OL,15,Fgroup-based child sexual exploitation
OL,16,Fare given more resources.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
